@node ReadMe! "P.D libraries readme and take notice!"

Amiga Frontier is a FREEware release, which means you can distribute
it anywhere at all, permission is given for use of inclusion on
CDROM whether it be Aminet or a P.D libraries own CDROM compilation.
You may copy this or give it to friends, but no fees other than for
diskcopying costs, price of a disk and postage & packaging may be charged.
Doing so would be breaking the law and it would piss me off a bit, so
don't do it.


Note to Readers
DMC is the product of AGAS productions, if you like DMC, and are interested
in using it, you MUST register for the full version. DO not even attempt to
rip this program, because we will find out eventually and we won't take it
lying down.
(although Molgy would- think about it)

Any comments, please send to:

Mark Seddon (A.F)
49 Rosslyn Drive
Moreton
Wirral
L46 OSU

Thanx.                            

Long live the Amiga
P.Cs should be extinct by now.

@endnode


